cst8284.triviatime

Class Controls

  • java.lang.Object
    • cst8284.triviatime.Controls

  • public class Controls
extends java.lang.Object
    This class controls what is displayed when the game starts. It displays the menu, menu items, and questions involved in the triviatime game.
